      <title>斯塔默推动人权计划，工党平衡工会和企业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/starmer-pushes-rights-plan-as-labour-balances-unions-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 誓言要推动英国雇员权利的全面改革，他的政府力求在下个月向议会提交一揽子重大工作改革方案之前赢得工会和企业的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/starmer-pushes-rights-plan-as-labour-balances-unions-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 12:04:27 GMT</pubDate>
